nodes.text: Nuendo Rash was a the captain of a YT-1300 light freighter operating during the Galactic Civil War. He owed twenty thousand credits to Jabba the Hutt which resulting in several of Jabba's enforcers firing at the spacer in Mos Eisley on Tatooine. In retaliation, Rash dropped several metric tons of grain onto Jabba's Palace against the advice of his crew, the cyborg First Mate Hutch and the Jedi Kaoln.
